API:

GET /games - получить открытые игры на данный момент

Response:
{
	"id": 1,
	"opened":true,
	"firstPlayer":"Ilya",
	"secondPlayer":null,
	"winner":null,
	"currentMove":null,
	"lastMove":-1,
	"isClosedByPlayer":false
}

POST /game/{gameId}/connect - подключиться к открытой игре

Request:
{
	"gameId":1,
	"name":"Ilya"
}

Response:
{
	"successful":true,
	"game":{
			"id":1,
			"opened":false,
			"firstPlayer":"Genadiy",
			"secondPlayer":"Ilya",
			"winner":null,
			"currentMove":"Genadiy",
			"lastMove":-1,
			"isClosedByPlayer":false
			}
}

POST /game/create - создать новую игру

Request:
{
	"name":"Ilya"
}

Response:
{
	"id":2,
	"opened":true,
	"firstPlayer":"Ilya",
	"secondPlayer":null,
	"winner":null,
	"currentMove":null,
	"lastMove":-1,
	"isClosedByPlayer":false
}

GET /game/{id}/state - получить текущее состояние игры

Response:
{
	"id": 1,
	"opened":false,
	"firstPlayer":"Ilya",
	"secondPlayer":"Anton",
	"winner":null,
	"currentMove":"Ilya",
	"lastMove":5,
	"isClosedByPlayer":false
}

POST /game/{id}/move - сделать ход

Request
{
	"cell":45,
	"name":"Ilya"
}

Response
{
	"successful":true,
	"cell":45
}

POST /game/{id}/exit - выйти из текущей игры

Request
{
	"name":"Ilya"
}

Response
{
	"id": 1,
	"opened":false,
	"firstPlayer":"Ilya",
	"secondPlayer":"Anton",
	"winner":null,
	"currentMove":"Ilya",
	"lastMove":5,
	"isClosedByPlayer":true	
}
